snippet.title: Office Hours: Agentic Document Extraction (Nov 20, 2025)
snippet.description:
The ADE Office Hours program is an open Q&A session designed to scale technical support for developers and users of LandingAI’s Agentic Document Extraction (ADE) solution. 

Office Hours sessions are:
• Informal
• Interactive
• Focused on helping users troubleshoot real-world challenges, explore integration patterns
• A way to get expert advice directly from the ADE team.

This program complements the structured webinars by focusing on engagement and community building—allowing participants to learn, share, and collaborate in an open environment.

*Chapters*
00:00: Intro
03:23: New features
07:15: Respond to questions submitted in advance 
36:07: DPT-2 mini
38:48: Builder program
40:22: Upcoming office hours
41:08 Async parsing and Parse Jobs

*Resources*
- Playground: https://va.landing.ai/demo/doc-extraction
- Docs: https://docs.landing.ai/ade/ade-overview
- Helper Scripts: https://github.com/landing-ai/ade-helper-scripts
- Blogs: https://landing.ai/resources
- Discord: https://discord.com/invite/RVcW3j9RgR
- Security & Compliance: https://landing.ai/security-at-landingai
- Trust Center: https://trust.landing.ai/
- Subscriptions & Pricing: https://landing.ai/pricing-agentic-apis
